{"tid":542254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塌工作台一死　 港珠澳橋三承建商罪成","createTime":"2018-01-27T09:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T06:35:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"904c9352189aeb7d855baa002c5501827f67c25d","tid":542254,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180127/20287110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F20287110&d=7OokyB%2F3QRM7rQz4CQKcnv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0ca01b98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F20287110&h=b97600cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180127/20287110</a><br />\n<br />\n塌工作台一死　<br />\n港珠澳橋三承建商罪成<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180127/large/27la3p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F27la3p6.jpg&h=746b7d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案發當日機器試吊近百噸重組件時疑不勝負荷，吊杆連橋面工作台被扯冧倒塌。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港珠澳大橋工人2014年10月試吊近百噸重預製石屎組件時，機器疑不勝負荷，吊杆連橋面工作台被扯冧倒塌，工人由15米高空墮地，1死4傷。大橋承建商及外判商被票控違反工業安全共55罪，經審訊後3間承建商共21罪成立，下周四判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒採取足夠步驟防止工人墮下<br />\n<br />\n合組聯營公司承建整項工程的大判中國港灣工程、寶嘉建築及威勝利香港，被判沒採取足夠步驟防止有人墮下等各7罪罪成。裁判官指使用機器前的檢查及覆檢工作，按地盤內部守則應由不同人士分開處理，但案發前由同一人包辦；工人爬上預製組件工作時，多於一人把安全帶同時扣在同一條救生索，亦屬違規。辯方曾指裝置當時不是用作起重，使用前毋須通過檢查及獲發特定准用證，但裁判官不接納。控方專家雖指起重裝置有設計缺陷，但法庭認同辯方專家指，3間承建商無法合理地預見有倒塌風險，故未能確保機器設備安全獲判罪脫。<br />\n<br />\n至於向聯營公司提供工人的分判商及僱用43歲男死者測量員謝道𤎜的雙裕工程有限公司，裁判官認為雙裕只需確保僱員受訓及知悉安全守則，法例不是要求它自行提供培訓，而專家證人指3間承建商的入職培訓足夠，故判雙裕罪脫。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TWS5154-5208/15<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"d44c7b1ff8d87f0a139863679c2f099817d034e2","tid":542254,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"到時全條橋都會冧啦 驚閪咩"},{"pid":"8140ef994e563102404c932811c8636232b7d538","tid":542254,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"判刑係點?"},{"pid":"a8ffbae3758fc11e800f365088e47aabdfe6bf8a","tid":542254,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8140ef994e563102404c932811c8636232b7d538","tid":542254,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"判刑係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"賠錢了事"},{"pid":"f3b35d56ce29559c0dec73471df0f4e33042247e","tid":542254,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8ffbae3758fc11e800f365088e47aabdfe6bf8a","tid":542254,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8140ef994e563102404c932811c8636232b7d538","tid":542254,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"判刑係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"賠錢了事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"安全主任嗰啲唔使坐監?<br />\n死人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8411dd9c6084316db359868b8984eb4873162c","tid":542254,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b35d56ce29559c0dec73471df0f4e33042247e","tid":542254,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8ffbae3758fc11e800f365088e47aabdfe6bf8a","tid":542254,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8140ef994e563102404c932811c8636232b7d538","tid":542254,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"判刑係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"賠錢了事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"安全主任嗰啲唔使坐監?<br />\n死人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"如果有事要坐監阿茂做"},{"pid":"ec047